into two kinds of people,

00:44:55.209 --> 00:44:57.750
those who divide the world into
two kinds of people and those

00:44:57.750 --> 00:45:00.080
who don't.

00:45:00.080 --> 00:45:03.520
It's part of the reason we have
a press that thinks there's

00:45:03.520 --> 00:45:04.891
two sides to every question.

00:45:04.891 --> 00:45:06.640
There are not two sides
to every question.

00:45:06.640 --> 00:45:07.515
There's 6, 12, 17, 3.

00:45:09.850 --> 00:45:12.660
It depends on the question.

00:45:12.660 --> 00:45:19.930
So the crazed idea of
